---
import PitchSlide from "../PitchSlide.astro";
---

<PitchSlide
	id="de-risking"
	title="De-Risking Your Investment"
	subtitle="11 years of proven business success"
	bgColor="var(--bg-secondary)"
>
	<div class="de-risking-content">
		<div class="risk-grid grid grid-3">
			<div class="risk-card card">
				<h3>Business History</h3>
				<p>
					Est. 2014 with over 250,000 meals delivered and
					hundreds of catering events for long-term corporate clients.
				</p>
				<div class="risk-stat">
					<span class="stat-number">250k+</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Meals Delivered</span>
				</div>
				<div class="risk-stat mt-3">
					<span class="stat-number">100s</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Catering Events</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="risk-card card">
				<h3>Physical Assets</h3>
				<p>
					Leased 6,500 sqft warehouse in Dubai Investment Park 2 with fully fitted
					commercial kitchen and professional media studio.
				</p>
				<div class="risk-stat">
					<span class="stat-number">6,500</span>
					<span class="stat-label">sqft Facility</span>
				</div>
				<div class="risk-stat mt-3">
					<span class="stat-number">135k</span>
					<span class="stat-label">AED Annual Rent</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="risk-card card">
				<h3>Financial Position</h3>
				<p>
					Current operation is slightly below break-even with monthly revenues of 
					~55,000 AED against operational costs of ~60,000 AED.
				</p>
				<div class="risk-stat">
					<span class="stat-number">~55k</span>
					<span class="stat-label">AED Monthly Revenue</span>
				</div>
				<div class="risk-stat mt-3">
					<span class="stat-number">~60k</span>
					<span class="stat-label">AED Burn Rate</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="expansion-section mt-12">
			<h3>Growth & Expansion Potential</h3>
			<div class="expansion-grid grid grid-3">
				<div class="expansion-card card">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="phase-icon">üöÄ</span>
						<h4>Franchise Model</h4>
					</div>
					<p>Ready-to-scale business model with proven operations and established client base across the UAE.</p>
					<div class="status-tag ready">Ready to Launch</div>
				</div>

				<div class="expansion-card card">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="phase-icon">üíª</span>
						<h4>Proprietary SaaS Platform</h4>
					</div>
					<p>Fully developed and operational software system for meal planning and delivery businesses.</p>
					<div class="status-tag built">Already Built</div>
				</div>

				<div class="expansion-card card">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="phase-icon">üåê</span>
						<h4>Market Expansion</h4>
					</div>
					<p>Established UAE presence with infrastructure in place for regional growth across the GCC.</p>
					<div class="status-tag ready">Positioned for Growth</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</PitchSlide>

<style>
	/* De-Risking Section */
	.risk-stat {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1rem;
		background-color: rgba(46, 196, 182, 0.1);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
	}

	.risk-card {
		height: 100%;
	}

	.expansion-card {
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		position: relative;
	}

	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-header h4 {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.status-tag {
		margin-top: auto;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.status-tag.built {
		background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
		color: rgb(6, 95, 70);
	}

	.status-tag.ready {
		background-color: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.15);
		color: rgb(55, 48, 163);
	}

	.expansion-phase {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.phase-icon {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 2.5rem;
		height: 2.5rem;
		background-color: var(--color-primary);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.mt-12 {
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}
	
	.mt-3 {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}
</style> 